query:
SELECT 
  s.id,
  s.name,
  COUNT(DISTINCT p.apiId) as api_count
FROM prices p
INNER JOIN services s ON p.serviceId = s.id
INNER JOIN sms_apis a ON p.apiId = a.id
WHERE p.countryId = 1
  AND a.active = 1
GROUP BY s.id, s.name
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT p.apiId) > 1
ORDER BY api_count DESC
LIMIT 10;
